be effective in improving estradiol level of postmenopausal osteoporotic female. 
The efficacy of anaerobic exercise was found to be more potent on estradiol 
level and lean mass than aerobic exercises as only 36 sessions of resisted 
exercises performed during a period of 12 weeks provided more significant result 
than 72 session of aerobic exercises.

